outputs.output_descr:
Joint Programme Outputs:
1. Crosscutting gender and racial dimensions of policies, programmes and public services expanded and enhanced;
2. Local and regional capacities for reinforcing promotion of gender and racial equality strengthened and integrated;
3. Egalitarian, plural and multiracial participation of women in public decision-making spaces strengthened and expanded;
4. Items relating to promotion of gender and racial equality featured and given prominence in the media.
